[normal]Innovative technologies 
[normal]must be used
[normal] in [developing] countries to 
[normal]prevent
[normal] them going down the path of inefficient products, as we have done. If the majority of the population insist on driving a car, countries like India and China 
[normal]should start
[normal] from the outset with a two-litre car
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
