[normal]I
[normal]'
[normal]m not asking people to become vegetarian. I
[normal]'
[normal]m telling them to eat less meat. Ther
[normal]e are huge benefits in eating less meat, and I tell everyone that you will be healthier, and so will be the planet. There are some societies in this world that are consuming excessive quantities of meat. That
[normal]'
[normal]s not desirable.
