[normal]The comments appear to be valid, but if followed through would require the thorny path of changing a plenary approved formulation. Yet the authors need 
[normal]to reflect and make a proposal 
[normal]that
[normal] will allow the needed steps by all IPCC actors and bodies, up to the plenary if necessary
[normal],
[normal] 
[normal]to become involved to resolve this issue
[normal] as felt appropriate by the author team.
